channel.title: Vote on the update you want to see next coming to Refined Power!
channel.description:
Chose what update you want to come next to Refined Power! all up to you my dudes! Have fun deciding which one you want next :slight_smile:
Poll ended next updates will be Modular power design (MDP), Battery power, toxic gas power, Reservoir power, and mk2 water turbine!
Happy building!
